The Old style Road construction window applies to the Original TT, Original TTD, TTDPatch, and OpenTTD Prior to 0.3.4 . For the new window, see [[en/Manual/Roadway construction]].

==Constructing Roads==
You can start constructing by pressing the road build button [[File:en/Manual html ma6d6c8c.png]] on the menu bar. Once clicked the Road Construction window pops up (Fig 1). 

<center>[[File:en/Road construction.png|center|none|frame|Fig 1. - The Original Road Build Window]]
</center>

==What do all these buttons do?==
The buttons are self-explanatory. From left to right:

:*[[File:en/Build road.png]] '''Build road buttons''': Builds a road in the selected direction, you can click and drag for all roads.
:*[[File:en/Clear title.png]] '''[[en/Manual/Landscaping|Clear land]] button'''
:*[[File:en/Lower land.png]] '''[[en/Manual/Landscaping|Lower land]] button'''
:*[[File:en/Raise land.png]] '''[[en/Manual/Landscaping|Raise land]] button'''
:*[[File:en/Build roaddepot.png]] '''Build [[en/Manual/Depots|depot]] button''': Opens the depot build window for you to select a depot direction to build.
:*[[File:en/Build busstation.png]] '''Build [[en/Manual/Stations#Bus Stations|bus stop]] button''': Opens the bus stop build window for you to select a bus stop direction to build.
:*[[File:en/Build truckstation.png]] '''Build [[en/Manual/Stations#Truck Stations|truck stop]] button''': Opens the truck stop build window for you to select a truck stop direction to build.
:*[[File:en/Build roadbridge.png]] '''Build [[en/Manual/Bridges|bridge]] button'''
:*[[File:en/Build roadtunnel.png]] '''Build [[en/Manual/Tunnels|tunnel]] button'''
:*[[File:en/Toggle clear active.png]] '''Toggle clear button''': When you select another tool and this you can remove that item.
:*[[File:en/Buy land.png]] '''Buy [[en/Manual/Land|land]] Button'''
